org.canova.image.recordreader

Class ImageNetRecordReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.canova.api.records.reader.BaseRecordReader
      • org.canova.image.recordreader.BaseImageRecordReader
        • org.canova.image.recordreader.ImageNetRecordReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.AutoCloseable, Configurable, RecordReader

    public class ImageNetRecordReader
extends BaseImageRecordReader
    Record reader to handle ImageNet dataset Built to avoid changing api at this time. Api should change to track labels that are only referenced by id in filename Creates a hashmap for label name to id and references that with filename to generate matching lables.
